## What's happening?
ClickHouse threads on {{host.name}} are spending a high percentage of time waiting for CPU scheduling. This indicates CPU saturation and will cause query latency to degrade.

## How to investigate
Check overall host CPU utilization. Review concurrent query load via `system.processes`. Consider scaling up CPU resources or reducing query concurrency.

